{"id":"api/core/global","title":"@angular/core/global","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/global\", \"name\": \"@angular/core/global\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/global/PACKAGE.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/global/PACKAGE.md\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n<header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n  <h1 id=\"angularcoreglobal\">@angular/core/global<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/global#angularcoreglobal\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n  <label class=\"api-type-label NaN\">entry-point</label>\n  \n  \n  \n</header>\n\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\"><p>Exposes a set of functions in the global namespace which are useful for debugging the current state\nof your application.\nThese functions are exposed via the global <code>ng</code> \"namespace\" variable automatically when you import\nfrom <code>@angular/core</code> and run your application in development mode. These functions are not exposed\nwhen the application runs in a production mode.</p>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  <h2 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"入口點的匯出\">入口點的匯出<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/global#入口點的匯出\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"entry-point-exports\">Entry point exports<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/global#entry-point-exports\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"函式\">函式<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/global#函式\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"functions\">Functions<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/global#functions\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/global/ngApplyChanges\">ng.applyChanges</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p translation-result=\"on\">把一個元件標記為需要檢查（OnPush 元件中），並且在本元件所屬的應用中同步執行執行變更檢測。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Marks a component for check (in case of OnPush components) and synchronously\nperforms change detection on the application this component belongs to.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetComponent\">ng.getComponent</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p translation-result=\"on\">檢索與給定 DOM 元素關聯的元件例項。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Retrieves the component instance associated with a given DOM element.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetContext\">ng.getContext</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p translation-result=\"on\">如果在嵌入式檢視中（比如 <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a></code> 或 <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a></code>），則檢索元素所屬的嵌入式檢視的上下文。否則，檢索其檢視中擁有該元素的元件的例項（在這種情況下，其結果與呼叫 <code><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetOwningComponent\" class=\"code-anchor\">getOwningComponent</a></code> 相同）。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">If inside an embedded view (e.g. <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a></code> or <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a></code>), retrieves the context of the embedded\nview that the element is part of. Otherwise retrieves the instance of the component whose view\nowns the element (in this case, the result is the same as calling <code><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetOwningComponent\" class=\"code-anchor\">getOwningComponent</a></code>).</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetDirectiveMetadata\">ng.getDirectiveMetadata</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p translation-result=\"on\">返回特定指令或元件例項的除錯（部分）元資料。該函式接受指令或元件的例項，並返回相應的元資料。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Returns the debug (partial) metadata for a particular directive or component instance.\nThe function accepts an instance of a directive or component and returns the corresponding\nmetadata.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetDirectives\">ng.getDirectives</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p translation-result=\"on\">檢索與給定 DOM 元素關聯的指令例項。不包括元件例項。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Retrieves directive instances associated with a given DOM node. Does not include\ncomponent instances.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetHostElement\">ng.getHostElement</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p translation-result=\"on\">檢索元件或指令例項的宿主元素。宿主元素是與指令的選擇器匹配的 DOM 元素。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Retrieves the host element of a component or directive instance.\nThe host element is the DOM element that matched the selector of the directive.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetInjector\">ng.getInjector</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p translation-result=\"on\">檢索與元素、元件或指令例項關聯的 <code><a href=\"api/core/Injector\" class=\"code-anchor\">Injector</a></code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Retrieves an <code><a href=\"api/core/Injector\" class=\"code-anchor\">Injector</a></code> associated with an element, component or directive instance.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetListeners\">ng.getListeners</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p translation-result=\"on\">檢索與 DOM 元素關聯的事件監聽器的列表。該列表包含宿主監聽器，但不包含在 Angular 上下文之外定義的事件監聽器（比如，透過 <code>addEventListener</code>）。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Retrieves a list of event listeners associated with a DOM element. The list does include host\nlisteners, but it does not include event listeners defined outside of the Angular context\n(e.g. through <code>addEventListener</code>).</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetOwningComponent\">ng.getOwningComponent</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p translation-result=\"on\">檢索其檢視中包含此 DOM 元素的元件例項。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Retrieves the component instance whose view contains the DOM element.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetRootComponents\">ng.getRootComponents</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p translation-result=\"on\">檢索與 DOM 元素，指令或元件例項關聯的所有根元件。根元件是由 Angular 引導啟動的元件。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Retrieves all root components associated with a DOM element, directive or component instance.\nRoot components are those which have been bootstrapped by Angular.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"結構\">結構<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/global#結構\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"structures\">Structures<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/global#structures\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/global/ComponentDebugMetadata\">ComponentDebugMetadata</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p translation-result=\"on\">給定元件例項的部分元資料。此資訊可能可用於除錯目的或工具。目前有以下欄位可用：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Partial metadata for a given component instance.\nThis information might be useful for debugging purposes or tooling.\nCurrently the following fields are available:</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/global/DirectiveDebugMetadata\">DirectiveDebugMetadata</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p translation-result=\"on\">給定指令例項的部分元資料。此資訊可能可用於除錯目的或工具。當前只有 <code>inputs</code> 和 <code>outputs</code> 元資料可用。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Partial metadata for a given directive instance.\nThis information might be useful for debugging purposes or tooling.\nCurrently only <code>inputs</code> and <code>outputs</code> metadata is available.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/core/global/Listener\">Listener</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p translation-result=\"on\"><code><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetListeners\" class=\"code-anchor\">getListeners</a></code> 返回的事件監聽器配置。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Event listener configuration returned from <code><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetListeners\" class=\"code-anchor\">getListeners</a></code>.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/global/ComponentDebugMetadata\n - api/core/global/DirectiveDebugMetadata\n - api/core/global/Listener\n - api/core/global/ngApplyChanges\n - api/core/global/ngGetComponent\n - api/core/global/ngGetContext\n - api/core/global/ngGetDirectiveMetadata\n - api/core/global/ngGetDirectives\n - api/core/global/ngGetHostElement\n - api/core/global/ngGetInjector\n - api/core/global/ngGetListeners\n - api/core/global/ngGetOwningComponent\n - api/core/global/ngGetRootComponents\n - guide/elements\n - guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants\n - guide/router-tutorial-toh\n - guide/testing-code-coverage\n - guide/upgrade\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common/NgFor\n - api/common/NgIf\n - api/core\n - api/core/Injector\n - api/core/global#angularcoreglobal\n - api/core/global#entry-point-exports\n - api/core/global#functions\n - api/core/global#structures\n - api/core/global#入口點的匯出\n - api/core/global#函式\n - api/core/global#結構\n - api/core/global/ComponentDebugMetadata\n - api/core/global/DirectiveDebugMetadata\n - api/core/global/Listener\n - api/core/global/ngApplyChanges\n - api/core/global/ngGetComponent\n - api/core/global/ngGetContext\n - api/core/global/ngGetDirectiveMetadata\n - api/core/global/ngGetDirectives\n - api/core/global/ngGetHostElement\n - api/core/global/ngGetInjector\n - api/core/global/ngGetListeners\n - api/core/global/ngGetOwningComponent\n - api/core/global/ngGetRootComponents\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/global/PACKAGE.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/global/PACKAGE.md\n-->"}